creator: ZP Group Inc.
descriptionHtml:
With the newest ZP app, it’s never been easier or more fun to transform your life and score big money! ZP’s powerful and personalized app includes inspirational stories and helpful tips based on your interests and a custom leaderboard to monitor your success. Featuring ZP Plus with more resources and hotlines, and ZP Store, where you can see the products our heroes recommend for great success.


Take the 21-Day ZP Challenge to meet your personal goals and you’ll be eligible for amazing cash prizes! All you have to do is make better choices in any of the categories that make sense for you: food, fitness, family and money. The best part is you decide what better choices can work for you. Start your ZP journey today!


You’re the boss

What defines a better choice is completely up to you — the “right way” to ZP is yours and yours alone. ZP supports you with encouragement, inspiration and tons of love at every step along the way!


NEW! Enjoy your personalized newsfeed

Every day, the ZP app customizes your newsfeed with helpful tips and uplifting stories selected just for you, based on your interests and goals.


NEW! Free support and guidance with ZP Plus

Benefit from free help and resources along with thousands of real-life stories to support you on your journey.


NEW! ZP Store has our heroes’ recommendations for your best success

ZP heroes share the things that worked for their better choice journey, including products that helped them reach their goals.


NEW! Chart your success

Your personal leaderboard tracks your progress and helps you stay motivated.


Be a star!

Share your story, photos and videos with us — and you might be featured on the ZP app.


Take ZP’s 21-Day Challenge

Once you click your first better choice — you’re part of the 21-Day Challenge. Make as many better choices as you like during a 21-day period and you’re eligible to enter to win cash awards from our giant prize pool.


The ZP Challenge contest is not affiliated with Apple, Inc. See Terms of Service and Contest Rules inside the app.

title: ZP Challenge

creator: ZP Group Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The Thrive ZP app makes it possible to transform your life, one small Better Choice at a time. It’s a behavior change coach in your pocket, encouraging you to take your well-being journey at your own pace and celebrate your successes along the way! Use the Thrive ZP app to commit to Better Choices in these areas of your life: Food, Fitness, Family, Money, Gratitude, and Sleep. Pick from a variety of easy-to-do Better Choices, or come up with your own.

Once you’ve decided on a Better Choice or two, start your 21-day Thrive ZP Challenge! Log your Better Choices each day (there’s no minimum or maximum) and enjoy all the positive benefits in your life. After 21 days, submit a short story about your Thrive ZP Challenge and enter for a chance to win part of $1,000,000 in cash prizes!

The opportunity to win isn’t even the best part of the Thrive ZP app — the app comes with a host of tools that can immediately boost your well-being and make you feel better. Plus, you’ll gain access to our supportive Thrive ZP community that will have your back at every step of your journey.

With the Thrive ZP app, you can read inspiring stories from community members like you who have changed their lives for the better, and hear their tips for incorporating Better Choices into your life. Use the calendar feature to log your Better Choices and track how long is left in your 21-day Challenge. And when you’re feeling stressed, you can turn to the Reset guide — a special feature that combines images, music, and uplifting quotes that will bring you joy and boost your mood in just 60 seconds. Make the Reset guide your own by uploading photos of friends, family, and pets, your favorite words of wisdom, and that upbeat song that never fails to make you feel good.

If you are a Walmart or Sam’s Club associate, the new Thrive ZP app will also connect you with the Walmart Cares well-being center — a hub of resources to support your personal and professional goals and connect you with a helping hand when you need it most.

The Thrive ZP app will completely transform your approach to well-being, one small Better Choice at a time. Join the Thrive ZP family today!
